OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,7,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Feeling
OL,8,Freasonably warm in any sunshine, but a
OL,9,Fchilly breeze along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be dry but clouding
OL,14,Fover across the west later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FMainly cloudy with rain
OL,17,Fspreading east for a time in the
OL,18,Fmorning. Drier in the afternoon with a
OL,19,Ffew showers, some brightness across
OL,20,Fthe west. Colder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
