OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome sunshine on Friday, patchy rain
OL,7,Fin the evening. Mainly dry on Saturday
OL,8,Falthough a few afternoon showers.
OL,9,FBreezy with showers on Sunday.
